00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:19,580
No matter what,

585
00:34:20,239 --> 00:34:23,900
you shouldn't interfere with His Majesty the Emperor's affairs.

586
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,360
His Majesty the Emperor.

587
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:33,199
A favored cabinet member of His Imperial Majesty,

588
00:34:33,199 --> 00:34:34,760
General Osumi Tsugio,

589
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:38,120
In the jurisdiction of the Sixth Air Base

590
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:41,719
died mysteriously in a plane crash.

591
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,580
His Majesty was not satisfied

592
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,440
and sent an investigator

593
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:48,480
to look into this accident.

594
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:51,239
Then the Control Faction sent a telegram

595
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:54,159
requesting the Metropolitan Police Department to investigate

596
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:56,480
the Emperor's investigator.

597
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:58,720
Am I correct?

598
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:03,160
I don't know what you're really up to.

599
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:06,040
Are you saying

600
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:10,160
that the suspect at the Sixth Air Base

601
00:35:11,040 --> 00:35:13,080
was personally sent by His Majesty?

602
00:35:14,640 --> 00:35:15,200
What you shouldn't know

603
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:16,840
is better left unknown.

604
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:21,840
The Emperor intentionally bypassed Imperial Headquarters

605
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:23,360
and sent down an official.

606
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,360
Naturally, some

607
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:28,080
officers of the Control Faction would be uncomfortable.

608
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:31,960
As an investigator from the Metropolitan Police,

609
00:35:32,560 --> 00:35:34,280
you've rashly come here without understanding the situation.

610
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:36,210
To verify this official's mission

611
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:38,480
and interfere with the investigation.

612
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:42,320
Is your Metropolitan Police Department

613
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:45,640
suspecting His Majesty the Emperor?

614
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:47,840
No, no, no.

615
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:50,160
The Tokyo Metropolitan Police received

616
00:35:50,160 --> 00:35:52,680
repeated requests from the Ministry of Finance

617
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:54,280
and Shanghai Garrison

618
00:35:55,520 --> 00:35:57,600
before sending me to Shanghai

619
00:35:58,040 --> 00:35:58,800
to verify the identity

620
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:00,530
of that special investigator.

621
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:03,850
So you're saying

622
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:07,890
you're all from the Imperial Guard Division?

623
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:26,920
Don't ask too many questions.

624
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:31,920
Forget my name and face.

625
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:34,700
All you need to know is that

626
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,360
these people are involved in

627
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:42,720
activities serving the interests of imperial power.

628
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,040
I understand.

629
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:55,520
So what do you plan to do with me?

630
00:36:58,520 --> 00:37:00,400
We've told you too much already.

631
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:01,890
To be honest.

632
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:05,120
Detaining you would be quite troublesome.

633
00:37:06,720 --> 00:37:08,280
We're consulting with the palace.

634
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:09,520
Let's see what my superiors

635
00:37:09,520 --> 00:37:10,720
decide to do with you.

636
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:30,700
Section Chief.

637
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:33,260
How should we handle this person?

638
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:36,680
Let's not execute him yet.

639
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:40,400
The Metropolitan Police Department has its difficulties too.

640
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:43,200
Let's consult with the palace again.

641
00:38:17,560 --> 00:38:22,160
These are the Colonel's files.

642
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:40,520
What you're doing now

643
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:42,120
is nothing short of treason.

644
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:45,320
You've also betrayed the Emperor.

645
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,360
Your Tokyo Metropolitan Police Department's Sixth Division

646
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,960
has allowed itself

647
00:38:49,720 --> 00:38:50,760
to be led

648
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,680
by military factions.

649
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:58,760
I truly don't understand the situation here.

650
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:03,040
You're really a troublemaker.

651
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:06,060
The palace wants us to give you

652
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:08,280
a chance to redeem yourself.

653
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:10,600
Three days.

654
00:39:11,240 --> 00:39:13,000
Can you handle these matters?

655
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,480
I understand.

656
00:39:18,280 --> 00:39:19,400
I'll do my best.

657
00:39:19,960 --> 00:39:20,720
Good.

658
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:23,640
Can you guarantee it?

659
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:27,800
Please trust me.

660
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:34,120
When you're done, go straight back to Tokyo.

661
00:39:34,480 --> 00:39:35,340
Did you hear me?

662
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:37,640
I understand.

663
00:39:56,720 --> 00:39:57,520
What is this?

664
00:39:58,600 --> 00:39:59,680
It states here

665
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:01,000
that you've committed

666
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:05,530
a capital offense by interfering with His Majesty the Emperor's investigation.

667
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,840
Sign here.

668
00:40:19,640 --> 00:40:21,160
I can't sign this.

669
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:25,720
I believe I can execute you right now.

670
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:30,130
Can I trust what you're saying?

671
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,410
I'll tell you one last time.

672
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:20,020
His Majesty doesn't want any unrest in the army.

673
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:23,480
If you don't keep your mouth shut,

674
00:41:23,720 --> 00:41:24,800
you're dead.

675
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,280
If you cause any unrest within the army,

676
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:30,520
you're also dead.

677
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,040
Understood.

678
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:53,200
Where do you want me to go?

679
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:54,400
The airport.

680
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:56,770
Someone will pick you up there.

681
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:02,320
Inspector.

682
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:04,770
I want you to remember this.

683
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,680
You've never seen us.

684
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,460
Never even seen any Imperial Guards.

685
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,480
Or any officers close to the Emperor.

686
00:42:13,200 --> 00:42:14,680
Keep your mouth shut.

687
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:18,720
Our people will be watching you at all times.

688
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:23,840
Do you understand?

689
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,160
I understand.
